# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:9
translate chinese cc7_5ae546b6:

    # pc "I've been thinking about my mom a lot lately."
    pc "最近我经常想起我妈妈。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:10
translate chinese cc7_e40d782f:

    # sc "Really? I don't think you've ever talked to me about your mother."
    sc "真的吗？我好像从未听你提起过你的母亲。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:11
translate chinese cc7_020f8e37:

    # pc "She died when I was young. Cancer."
    pc "她在我很小的时候就去世了。是癌症。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:13
translate chinese cc7_3238c9b9:

    # sc "Oh, I'm so sorry."
    sc "哦，真抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:14
translate chinese cc7_e21408a5:

    # pc "It's okay. It was a long time ago. I don't get sad about it very often anymore."
    pc "没关系。那是很久以前的事了。我现在很少为此感到难过了。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:15
translate chinese cc7_0ee9c48b:

    # pc "But I do still think about her all the time."
    pc "但我还是时常想起她。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:16
translate chinese cc7_4b0e108d:

    # pc "How she looked when she was happy."
    pc "想起她开心时的样子。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:17
translate chinese cc7_e818e53f:

    # pc "I miss her like crazy."
    pc "我特别想她。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:18
translate chinese cc7_348e7c78:

    # sc "I bet. It's hard to lose a parent. To lose that support that you always counted on."
    sc "我猜也是。失去父母很难受。失去了那个你一直依赖的依靠。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:19
translate chinese cc7_da14e0fd:

    # pc "Yeah. I can sort of understand how somebody would do some pretty crazy things to get back a person that they loved and lost."
    pc "是啊。我多少能理解，为什么有人会为了挽回失去的挚爱而做出些疯狂的事。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:20
translate chinese cc7_6ae9b1e8:

    # sc "Like what?"
    sc "比如什么？"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:21
translate chinese cc7_cf6a6f42:

    # pc "Nothing specific. You know the stories where somebody does something like bury their loved one in a pet cemetery, or trade their soul to bring back somebody they lost."
    pc "没什么具体的。你知道那些故事吧，有人会把亲人埋在宠物墓地里，或者出卖灵魂来换回逝去的亲人。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:22
translate chinese cc7_bc5b1a1e:

    # sc "Yeah, but those are just stories."
    sc "是啊，但那只是故事。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:23
translate chinese cc7_6069639a:

    # pc "Right. I'm just saying that I can understand those people."
    pc "对。我只是说我能理解那些人。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:24
translate chinese cc7_be8ce256:

    # pc "If it hurts me this bad, I can only imagine the hell my dad must have been going through."
    pc "如果我这么难受，我简直不敢想象我爸当时经历了怎样的煎熬。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:25
translate chinese cc7_c65da1ae:

    # sc "Yeah, it must have been tough."
    sc "是啊，那一定很难熬。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:27
translate chinese cc7_9b035c6b:

    # pc "Well, I better head to class."
    pc "嗯，我得去上课了。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:28
translate chinese cc7_a937fabe:

    # sc "Are you sure you're okay?"
    sc "你确定没事吗？"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:29
translate chinese cc7_ab3c6ff4:

    # pc "Yeah, I'm okay. Thanks, Gertrude."
    pc "嗯，我没事。谢谢你，格特鲁德。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:30
translate chinese cc7_db3e498b:

    # sc "Is it okay if I give you a hug?"
    sc "我能抱抱你吗？"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:37
translate chinese cc7_d7205a0a:

    # "I stand up and she wraps her arms around me, holding me close."
    "我站起身，她双臂环住我，紧紧地搂着我。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:38
translate chinese cc7_5382d9b7:

    # sc "You're a good guy, [pcname]."
    sc "你是个好人，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:39
translate chinese cc7_a9c4bfe1:

    # sc "And it's okay to think about your mom and be sad."
    sc "想念你妈妈、感到难过，这很正常。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:40
translate chinese cc7_97139c8b:

    # sc "It's okay to have those feelings."
    sc "有这些感受，没什么不对的。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:41
translate chinese cc7_c8da6d69:

    # pc "Thanks, Gertrude."
    pc "谢谢你，格特鲁德。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:42
translate chinese cc7_2fa61200:

    # sc "You take care of yourself. Okay, [pcname]?"
    sc "你要保重。好吗，[pcname]？"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:43
translate chinese cc7_5bc44b07:

    # pc "I will."
    pc "我会的。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:45
translate chinese cc7_c1e718d8:

    # sc "You're right. Let's keep this professional."
    sc "你说得对。咱们还是保持专业关系吧。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:47
translate chinese cc7_855b480c:

    # sc "I'll see you next time, [pcname]."
    sc "下次见，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:52
translate chinese cc7_d7205a0a_1:

    # "I stand up and she wraps her arms around me, holding me close."
    "我站起身，她双臂环住我，紧紧地搂着我。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:53
translate chinese cc7_5382d9b7_1:

    # sc "You're a good guy, [pcname]."
    sc "你是个好人，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:54
translate chinese cc7_a9c4bfe1_1:

    # sc "And it's okay to think about your mom and be sad."
    sc "想着你妈妈而感到难过，这很正常。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:55
translate chinese cc7_97139c8b_1:

    # sc "It's okay to have those feelings."
    sc "有这些感受，没什么不对的。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:56
translate chinese cc7_c8da6d69_1:

    # pc "Thanks, Gertrude."
    pc "谢谢你，格特鲁德。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:57
translate chinese cc7_2fa61200_1:

    # sc "You take care of yourself. Okay, [pcname]?"
    sc "你要保重。好吗，[pcname]？"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:58
translate chinese cc7_5bc44b07_1:

    # pc "I will."
    pc "我会的。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/7 - Mom.rpy:59
translate chinese cc7_da7d5c01:

    # "With that, I leave her office and head to class."
    "说完，我走出她的办公室，前往教室。"

